        <h1 class="display">I build the systems that make<br>GTM teams <span class="hl">do their best work.</span></h1>
        <p>I started in marketing analytics — building dashboards, cleaning messy data, and learning to make numbers tell a story through SQL and Tableau. That foundation took me into program management at a Series C/D company, where I spent two years building high-volume sales processes and learning what actually breaks when you try to scale simultaneously.</p>
        <p>In my current role as Lead Revenue Operations at Growfin, I work across Marketing, Sales, and CS and treat it as one connected system. My view on RevOps is straightforward: it’s not a back-end support function — it’s the infrastructure that determines whether a company can actually scale.</p>
      </div>
